<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Key-Repeat on Tech In Sight</title><link>https://techinsight.pages.dev/tags/key-repeat/</link><description>Recent content in Key-Repeat on Tech In Sight</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 21 Nov 2020 22:48:25 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://techinsight.pages.dev/tags/key-repeat/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>macOS设置Key Repeat和Delay Until Repeat</title><link>https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/macos%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEkey-repeat%E5%92%8Cdelay-until-repeat/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Nov 2020 22:48:25 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/macos%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEkey-repeat%E5%92%8Cdelay-until-repeat/</guid><description>&lt;p>macOS上用Vim觉得很卡顿，不流畅，终于找到原因了。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>有两个相关设置
&lt;img src="https://techinsight.pages.dev/images/2020-11-21-22-50-28.png"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这两个把&lt;code>Key Repeat&lt;/code>设置到最快，把&lt;code>Delay Until Repeat&lt;/code>设置到最短，但实际上这么设置之后还是不够，再小就不能通过配置页面设置了，只能通过命令行设置了。我觉得合适的配置是这样的&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">defaults write -g InitialKeyRepeat -int 10
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">defaults write -g KeyRepeat -int 1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>这样之后再操作就明显流畅多了。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>